txt.en: The Trév Duvárdain at the encampment of Tâg Fógarrach remain loyal servants of the Iron Crown. All those at Tâg Fógarrach threaten the safety of Gundabad and must be defeated.

Tâg Fógarrach can be found in western Câr Bronach.\n\nYou should defeat foes at Tâg Fógarrach.
